						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up in the village.</p>						

						<p>1593 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription is dated Śaka 1515, Vijaya, Chaitra śu. 1, corresponding to A.D. 1593, March 23, Friday.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to Bīragāuṁḍa at Hosahaḷḷi. The details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
